text: Relapse is the sixth studio album by American rapper, Eminem. Relapse was released on May 15, 2009. It was produced by Dr. Dre, Eminem, Dawaun Parker, Mark Batson, Trevor Lawrence, Doc Ish, Boi-1da. The album was given 4 out of 5 stars by Allmusic. ==Songs== ==References== Category:2009 albums Category:Eminem albums Category:Aftermath Entertainment albums Category:Grammy Award-winning albums Category:Interscope Records albums Category:Shady Records albums
